    "title": "Hasira ya Mungu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "hasira ya mungu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu ni mwenye haki na mwenye haki katika hukumu zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11\">Zaburi 7:11</a>). Anajibu kwa hasira ya haki dhidi ya dhambi na ukosefu wa haki. Hasira ya Mungu si kama ya mwanadamu. Si mlipuko wa kihisia au kupoteza udhibiti. Ni jibu lake kamilifu na takatifu kwa uovu. Watu waovu wanaendelea kufanya makosa na wanastahili hukumu yake (tazama<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:5\"> 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:9\">21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:7\">56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:13\">59:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:24\">69:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:6\">79:6</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">Warumi 1:18</a>). Ingawa Mungu ni mvumilivu na si mwepesi wa hasira, hataruhusu uovu kuendelea milele bila kuuzuia (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">86:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8\">103:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:8\">145:8</a>).</p><p>Waandishi wa Zaburi waliona kutoroka kwa Israeli kutoka Misri kama somo kuhusu hasira ya Mungu. Mungu alionyesha hasira yake dhidi ya Wamisri huku akiwalinda watu wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:49-Ps78:50\">Zaburi 78:49–50</a>). Hata hivyo, wakati wa safari yao kupitia nyikani, kutotii kwa Israeli kulisababisha hasira ya Mungu, na wakakabili hukumu yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:31\">78:31</a>;<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:29\"> 106:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:32\">32</a>).</p><p>Kutokana na hili, Mungu aliahidi kwamba kizazi kisichotii hakitaingia mahali pake pa pumziko (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:8-Ps95:11\">Zaburi 95:8–11</a>). Kwa hiyo walikufa jangwani. Hata hivyo, Mungu alizuia hasira yake na hakuiangamiza Israeli kabisa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:38\">78:38</a>).</p><p>Vivyo hivyo, katika kipindi cha Waamuzi na wafalme, watu wa Mungu mara nyingi hawakutii na walifanya mambo maovu. Kwa sababu hiyo, katika hasira yake, Mungu aliruhusu nguvu za kigeni kuwatawala na kuwapeleka uhamishoni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:5-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:5–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:20-2Kgs25:21\">24:20–25:21</a>). Hata hivyo, Mungu hakuruhusu watu wake kuangamizwa kabisa.</p><p>Wakati watu wa Mungu wanapofanya dhambi na kuhisi hasira yake, inaweza kuwaongoza kutubu. Uzoefu huu wa maumivu ya kihisia unaweza kuleta furaha kubwa katika rehema na wema wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:5\">Zaburi 30:5</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:11\">Waebrania 12:5–11</a>).</p><p>Agano Jipya linaeleza wazi kwamba watu wote walikuwa chini ya ghadhabu ya Mungu kwa sababu ya dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:1-Eph2:3\">Waefeso 2:1–3</a>). Hata hivyo, katika upendo wake, Mungu alimtuma Mwana wake, Yesu Kristo, ambaye alitoa maisha yake kwa ajili ya dhambi zetu ili tuweze kupatanishwa na Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6-Rom5:11\">Warumi 5:6–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">Waefeso 2:4–5</a>). Wale wanaomgeukia Mungu kwa imani wataepuka adhabu inayokuja katika hukumu ya ulimwengu ya baadaye. Hatimaye, Yesu, ambaye ni Mwokozi na Hakimu, ataleta haki ya Mungu dhidi ya waovu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:5-Ps2:9\">Zaburi 2:5–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:17\">Ufunuo 6:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11-Rev19:16\">19:11–16</a>). Mungu atashughulikia uovu wote kwa uamuzi, ikiwa ni pamoja na adui wake mkuu, shetani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7-Rev20:15\">Ufunuo 20:7–15</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunzia Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:5-Ps2:9\">Zaburi 2:5–9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:1\">6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:6\">7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11-Ps7:13\">11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:9\">21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:9\">27:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:5\">30:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:1-Ps38:10\">38:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https:/